Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:10.91,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,240)}どれだけ　近づいても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:13.25,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(240,240)}(Give it up Give it up)
